{"tid":1315450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警察隊員佐級協會促管理層須確保執勤警員人身安全","createTime":"2019-07-14T14:01:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T05:34:55.000Z","uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"db95809786afef45d6933f6e6e704d6aabcfb12e","tid":1315450,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T14:01:44.000Z","msg":"警察隊員佐級協會促管理層須確保執勤警員人身安全<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1468298_1_20190714153612.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1468298_1_20190714153612.jpg&h=83445490&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港警察隊員佐級協會，促請警務處處長及管理層必須確保執勤警員的人身安全及心理健康，除非管理層有信心，戰術及裝備等能確保執勤人員行動中的安全，否則不應指派人員執行可能受傷的任務或到危險地方執勤。<br />\n<br />\n主席林志偉在信中強調，並非質疑警隊管理層的行動決定，又說近期看到不少人員執勤時受傷，甚至面對危及生命安全的情況，激進示威者違法行為愈演愈烈，已大大超越文明社會可以接受的程度，使用懷疑腐蝕性液體的水彈、鐵枝及磚頭等攻擊警察；近日更包圍警察，以雨傘等攻擊，部分被圍困的警察只能以血肉之軀捱打。<br />\n<br />\n員佐級協會今日召開緊急執委會會議，商討應對方案。協會說如果情況沒有改善，會徵詢律師意見，尋求能夠更有效保障人員安全的方法。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1468298-20190714.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1468298-20190714.htm&d=uli%2BLK8ypwQfiBTSi%2FGP9%2FQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=432287bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1468298-20190714.htm&h=5b2a1718\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1468298-20190714.htm</a>"},{"pid":"c82dbf1644e97cc15c2833327817cd8a6faa814d","tid":1315450,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T14:03:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eaf2f707b276d5e19139e0dbc88882aae9641cf","tid":1315450,"uid":64193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T14:05:04.000Z","msg":"罷工囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ddddbd7f4197f5ca897ed885459c7150c05227a","tid":1315450,"uid":42967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T14:06:28.000Z","msg":"FULL GEAR <br />\n<br />\n人身安全 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c4f9c0df14926a1a4dc40488037b96ed2260a8d","tid":1315450,"uid":4964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T14:07:26.000Z","msg":"轉用中國製裝備囉"},{"pid":"a217c069a869be5a98490b8d0d4f8f235b91cc3c","tid":1315450,"uid":54256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T14:09:10.000Z","msg":"屌你老母比你拎咁高人工就係要拎條命黎搏嫁啦<br />\n垃撚圾"},{"pid":"abe66b063a0f4341a8ff8b83f8215a5c2bfd3808","tid":1315450,"uid":21592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T14:18:38.000Z","msg":"呢個協會無晒紀律, 鬼打鬼"},{"pid":"1769f06bfa4dafc385f65af5843c21340fc91d95","tid":1315450,"uid":42250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:34:55.000Z","msg":"究竟係藍衫定白衫？喂盧偉聰你含撚啦屌你老母！扮傻！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/diObzT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/diObzT</a>"}]}